# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../effects.rst:322
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Parent` property of an effect sets the initial keyframe "
"values to a parent effect. For example, if many effects all point to the "
"same parent effect, they will inherit all their initial properties, such as "
"font size, font color, and background color for a ``Caption`` effect. In the "
"example of many ``Caption`` effects using the same Parent effect, it is an "
"efficient way to manage a large number of these effects."
